Class MyBigDecimal

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.veos.MyBigDecimal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBigValue

    public class MyBigDecimal
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBigValue
    Data class to handle operations involving large numbers. Encapsulates a BigDecimal, and supports operations to add, multiply, etc. with other instances.
